60
00:03:52,580 --> 00:03:54,180
<font color=#FFFF00>akan alasan kau dipekerjakan di sini.</font>

61
00:03:55,980 --> 00:03:57,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau sampai terjadi kesalahan,</font>

62
00:03:59,080 --> 00:04:00,090
