77
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:51,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang itu...</font>

78
00:04:51,770 --> 00:04:53,870
<font color=#FFFF00>..adalah Pengacara spesialis gagal.</font>

79
00:04:53,870 --> 00:04:55,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Pengacara seperti itu sungguh ada?</font>

80
00:04:55,440 --> 00:04:58,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Izinnya hampir dicabut,
