81
00:04:58,410 --> 00:05:00,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebab itu, dia tidak diizinkan menangani kasus besar.</font>

82
00:05:00,780 --> 00:05:02,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada beberapa pengacara lain seperti dia.</font>

83
00:05:02,710 --> 00:05:05,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, kenapa firma kalian membutuhkan orang seperti dia?</font>

84
00:05:05,620 --> 00:05:07,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena dia pengacara spesialis gagal!</font>

85
00:05:08,950 --> 00:05:11,960
