<font color=#FFFF00>kau sudah tahu?</font>

101
00:05:56,570 --> 00:05:58,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang saya sedang menyelidikinya.</font>

102
00:05:58,340 --> 00:05:59,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Aigooya...</font>

103
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:02,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Kutebak, banyak sekali yang kau pikirkan saat ini.</font>

104
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:05,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun, akibat kasus Park Eung Mo,</font>

105
