154
00:08:41,770 --> 00:08:43,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu sebabnya.</font>

155
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:46,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebab itu, setidaknya dia harus melihat wajahku dulu.</font>

156
